title: Recv'd call & there's a ! appear'g where callr ID/ spam call is normally displayed. Whats that mean?
content: I tried to research online what ! Symbol stands for when rcv'g calls, but found nothing yet. Normally my phone will indicate "spam" or caller ID  when I rcv calls but I've never seen ! Symbol appear before till now. What does that mean?
